DynamicallyShuffledBag<Item> - Class in demos.bags
A DynamicallyShuffledBag is a Bag which, very much like a RandomAccessBag, shakes its contents completely (pseudo-) randomly.
DynamicallyShuffledBag() - Constructor for class demos.bags.DynamicallyShuffledBag
This constructor is used to initialize the bag with full pseudorandom capabilities for shaking and the default starting capacity.
DynamicallyShuffledBag(int) - Constructor for class demos.bags.DynamicallyShuffledBag

DynamicallyShuffledBag(int, long) - Constructor for class demos.bags.DynamicallyShuffledBag

DynamicallyShuffledBag(long) - Constructor for class demos.bags.DynamicallyShuffledBag
